		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/玻瑞亚斯之影.assets/Image_14.png')" x="1392" y="586">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/玻瑞亚斯之影.assets/Image_15.png')" x="1392" y="1065">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/玻瑞亚斯之影.assets/Image_16.png')" x="1392" y="1353">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="398" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">玻瑞亚斯蓄力吐出冰球，造成<span color="#99ffff">30%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1151" width="441" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">玻瑞亚斯嗥叫，并召唤大中小型3个<span textDecoration="underline">冰平台</span><span>，玻瑞亚斯率先跃入最大的平台，造成</span><span color="#99ffff">10%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>，并附属「</span><span textDecoration="underline">坚冰</span><span>」；所有平台均出现一枚「</span><span textDecoration="underline">未熄的战火</span><span>」；周围的</span><span color="#bfffff">空气开始变得寒冷</span><span>，每2s对角色造成</span><span color="#99ffff">5%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1439" width="423" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">玻瑞亚斯召唤「<span textDecoration="underline">蕴光孤狼</span><span>」及其狼魂，自身消失并附属「</span><span textDecoration="underline">永冬</span><span>」，同时场地</span><span color="#bfffff">空气变冷</span><span>，持续出现下落冰棱，造成</span><span color="#99ffff">20%</span><span>伤害；击败孤狼后玻瑞亚斯重新出现。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#2686a2" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#2686a2">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="424" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">玻瑞亚斯抬起身子，随后扑下，产生大范围的冰冲击波，造成<span color="#99ffff">30%</span><span>伤害。<br/>本技能抬身与扑下动作较「白草凇花」慢。本技能存在盲区，位于玻瑞亚斯正前方的一小块区域。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1439" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">玻瑞亚斯使用尾巴持续对玩家发射大量冰锥，共12枚，每枚造成<span color="#99ffff">10%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/玻瑞亚斯之影.assets/Image_17.png')" x="719" y="810">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/玻瑞亚斯之影.assets/Image_18.png')" x="720" y="1353">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="66" y="1104" width="441" height="289" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">在试炼之前，玻瑞亚斯的攻击力<span color="#ffbfbf">降低40%</span><span>。<br/>冰平台：由玻瑞亚斯召唤，由低到高为小中大三个，需要使用</span><span color="#bfffcc">「法尔伽」</span><span>的长按战技飞上去；平台出现期间，将持续造成</span><span color="#99ffff">20%</span><span>伤害。<br/>坚冰：</span><span color="#99ffff">12冻</span><span>盾，可伤害转化，存在时</span><span color="#bfffff">空气极寒</span><span>，击破来使玻瑞亚斯结束空气极寒，提前结束试炼，并推进到下一个试炼。<br/>永冬：</span><span color="#99ffff">40冻</span><span>盾，存在时</span><span color="#bfffff">空气极寒</span><span>，不可直接击破，击败「蕴光孤狼」以击破该盾。<br/>蕴光孤狼：与大世界版本类似，生命值</span><span color="#ffdfbf">445203</span><span>(12.0F)，攻击力</span><span color="#ffdfbf">7613</span><span>(4.0B2)；狼魂为</span><span color="#99ffff">12冻</span><span>盾，也是刚需</span><span color="#ff9999">火扩散</span><span>破盾。<br/>未熄的战火：试炼1后出现，接触可恢复</span><span color="#bfffbf">25%生命值</span><span>并</span><span color="#ffdfbf">重置CD</span><span>，集齐3枚可使法尔伽「狂飙突进」状态下染火，持续14.5s；战火每隔9s在玩家附近出现，每枚寿命20s。<br/>试炼1持续约80s，在其恢复至试炼2出现之前，玻瑞亚斯锁血。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="65" y="629" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="40" fontStyle="italic" fontWeight="normal" color="#99ffff" width="312" height="43" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="40" fontStyle="italic" color="#99ffff">无铭染血之狼灵</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#99e5ff" distance="16" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
